{"tid":1400874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家請冷靜 從今以後唔好守 見狗即走 打遊擊","createTime":"2019-08-03T13:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:44:59.000Z","uid":229436,"like":159,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"af965cc040f7060dfdf5352dc8143cf821a0ee3e","tid":1400874,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"守路實在係無意思<br />\n我唔知係咪有鬼故意帶頭守定點<br />\n但咁多次歷史的教訓<br />\n守路係難守 無意義 同時你唔係做攻方 你守黎無意思 <br />\n重點係 政府唔撚你理訴求係咩阿<br />\n<br />\n我地依家根本無能力搶點<br />\n你話攻入差館 同時多區都搶左黎守又唔同<br />\n但我地唔係呀 條路咪都無 亦都無車幫你BLOCK狗<br />\n<br />\n做義士 不做死士 <br />\n機場涼冷氣個影響力仲大阿大家"},{"pid":"37d11210fbcad3bcf688d21cc559500e221283fe","tid":1400874,"uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係認真 放棄條路啦好嗎<br />\n要守路一定要準備好多先有用<br />\n打三國一定要有<br />\n運輸車 大型物資/車BLOCK路 仲有令對方埋唔到黎的武力 缺一不可"},{"pid":"c99ba6968731ddf1d727968f6b29974a1609de3c","tid":1400874,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d866fd4b85eeb96e267ea2dd224294ca04cdce6d","tid":1400874,"uid":26813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">sorry借位宣傳<br />\n推俾前線手足睇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［前線路障快閃團］簡易快速拆鐵欄攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4572be0f8ceffeeffae0d50e3c931ea0582ecce","tid":1400874,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"轉場再撚過"},{"pid":"87ab795a9b3869f46547f1333581b377bab8cd04","tid":1400874,"uid":287619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:02:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21515136767a491f5bb459f779a28074da94a951","t